<lb ed="C I" n="0117b01"/><p id="pI01p0117b0101">大魏武定二年歲次甲子二月丙辰朔十六日辛<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">未</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">自</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">感</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear>□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">心</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">思</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b02"/>八人。一佛二菩薩大通<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">智</unclear>勝。有二太子。有八天人。二寶塔。倒龍師子。諸天花<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">琰</unclear>。．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b03"/>夫叡<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">軌</unclear>沖<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">玄</unclear>。非至真無以體其元。寂談玄廓。非正覺豈能識其趣。是以群生若．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b04"/>之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">慈</unclear>。像法遺誨。不墜惡道。拔以幽苦。於是闡提含生。同悟可尋。苦空難寄。審世非常。咸□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">後</unclear>□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b05"/>海。非輕能所竭。有維那王<note n="0117001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30750;＝貳【史】</note><app n="0117001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">貳</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30750;</rdg></app>郎。綰率法義三百人等。信心崇道。識鑒<note n="0117002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30751;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0117002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30751;</rdg></app><note n="0117003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30752;＝遠【史】</note><app n="0117003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30752;</rdg></app>。唱<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">情</unclear>先<note n="0117004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30753;＝發【史】</note><app n="0117004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">發</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30753;</rdg></app>。積微<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">至</unclear>廣。傾竭．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b06"/>使合門眷屬。願令從心。後以<note n="0117005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30822;＝靈【史】</note><app n="0117005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">靈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30822;</rdg></app>鑒。化容侍身。琴瑟箜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">篌</unclear>。簫笛<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鼓</unclear>樂。倒龍花琰。備如<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">詳</unclear>目。願使天下．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0117b07"/>義諸人并家眷屬。剋唱萇年。常以佛會。面奉聖顏。彌勒下生。願登上首。法義兄弟題名刊石．．．
